Kenapa nulis soal itu? Karena baru aja ngerasain perubahan vibe yang drastis dari seseorang di inner circle. Sedrastis kehilangan minat bahkan buat sekedar ngobrol basa basi.

Fun? Nggak juga. Hemat waktu, iya. Tapi menyiksa pas harus bertahan sama orang yang vibenya nggak cocok. Daaan semua ini terasa tanpa diminta, tanpa dicari, tanpa disengaja. It comes instantly everytime I meet someone new.
"This person will get along with me". "This person won't". And sometimes, it's "Looks like a special chapter is on the making".
I don't mean to be superstitious (I don't even think this is superstitious at all), but I can say I understand the language of vibe. This helped me a lot to filter my circle.
